{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bb09a8b72f","title":"致贺龙、关向应、滕代远等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"22de3f2e14","index":0,"year":1940,"month":1,"day":20,"articleId":"bb09a8b72f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d0a2337495","name":"贺龙","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji14.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji14":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"02ef9acdd9","type":"paragraph","text":"致贺龙、关向应、滕代远等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"bb09a8b72f"},{"id":"12b5d6a4c5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年1月20日）旧派在晋西北失败后，有可能再调兵反攻晋西北或由日寇进攻晋西北，而旧军则袭击后方。同时图必与中央更加勾结，以谋夺取晋东南。因此普西北必以突击方式，抓紧目前有利时机，进行一切工作。一切应当快做，退缓就会失掉时机。晋西北新政权总机关应当立即成立，意快意好。晋西北新政权的各种政策仿效普察算边区。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"bb09a8b72f"}],"page":{"id":"93e3bf7bba","publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"bb09a8b72f","start":351,"end":351}}}},"__N_SSG":true}